original_title: Jackson Browne: I'll Do Anything - Live In Concert
overview: Filmed November 14, 2012 at the Paramount Theater, Denver, Colorado, Jackson Browne’s "I’ll Do Anything - Live in Concert"  includes seventeen performances and features his longtime band mates Fritz Lewak and Val McCallum, along with Sara Watkins, Sean Watkins and Tyler Chester
title: Jackson Browne: I'll Do Anything - Live In Concert
